Modifications made in this fork (Apache-2.0 §4 change notice):

  - Phase 6 (Validation) rewritten as a bounded convergence loop:
    added 6-0 loop control (hard/soft gates, stopping conditions,
    budget guardrails), 6-L loop body, 6-7 coverage critic
    (loop-until-dry), 6-8 termination report; 6-1..6-6 converted to
    gate-score-returning steps; adversarial trigger verification option.
  - Phase 7 (Evolution) rewritten as a self-improvement loop:
    added 7-0 loop control with human approval gate and Phase 6
    re-validation (regression rollback); 7-1 telemetry signal
    collection; 7-4 automatic evolution triggers.
  - Added references/validation-loop.md (loop control detail,
    domain-tier presets, state schema, prompt templates).
  - Budget-allocation refinements: execution test (6-3) runs only
    after hard gates pass; coverage critic (6-7) uses a separate
    budget (C_budget) to prevent starvation.
